dct_title_s: Map of Hunterdon County, New Jersey : entirely from original surveys
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. "Entered according to an Act of Congress in the year 1851 by L. Van Derveer ... " Wall map. Insets: Plan of Flemington -- Plan of Lambert-ville, Hunterdon County, New Jersey. Includes views of the State Capitol, Trenton and County buildings; shows names of property owners.
